extends ../_modal

block content
  .panel-body
    p.lead.
      Welcome to Gossamer, a place to try experimental browser features.
    ul
      li Only verified <a href="http://mozillians.org">Mozillians</a> can publish experiments here.
      li Gossamer sends anonymous metrics about usage, performance, and errors to experimenters.
      li Your session (e.g. history, bookmarks) in Gossamer is separate from your normal browser session.
    p Ready to get started?
    a.btn.btn-lg.btn-default.btn-primary.btn-block(
      href='/user/oauth?redirect=' + encodeURIComponent('/my/index.html')
    ) Log in with GitHub
